The signal reached the personal monitor of High Researcher Photonis.
He was a bulky and awkward looking transformer, but his processor was
the kind of thing that made Lord Jotunn smile with pleasure with the
things it produced. Thus, a pod nearby attracted his attention. He
left the base on the four legs of his robot mode, then outside,
tranformed into a high velocity hovercraft, and he sped to the pod.
